{
  "bookId": "laozi-heshanggong-wiki",
  "num": 7,
  "title": "第七章（韜光）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "天長地久，"
    },
    {
      "text": "天地所以能長且久者，以其不自生，"
    },
    {
      "text": "故能長生。"
    },
    {
      "text": "是以聖人後其身，"
    },
    {
      "text": "而身先，"
    },
    {
      "text": "外其身，"
    },
    {
      "text": "而身存。"
    },
    {
      "text": "非以其無私邪。"
    },
    {
      "text": "故能成其私。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "說天地長生久壽，以喻教人也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 16
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "天地所以獨長且久者，以其安靜，施不求報，不如人居處，汲汲求自饒之利，奪人以自與也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以其不求生，故能長生不終也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "先人而後己也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "天下敬之，先以為長。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "薄己而厚人也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "百姓愛之如父母，神明祐之若赤子，故身常存。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 7
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人為人所愛，神明所祐，非以其公正無私所致乎。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "人以為私者，欲以厚己也。聖人無私而己自厚，故能成其私也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
